# Title: Steganography Extract Files with Steghide
# Author: Pawel Mazur
# Date: 2021-09-11
# Level: low
# Description: Detects extraction of files with usage of steghide binary, the adversaries may use this technique to prevent the detection of hidden information.
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1027.003
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/auditd/execve/lnx_auditd_steghide_extract_steganography.yml

a0="steghide" a1="extract" a2="-sf" a3 IN ("*.jpg", "*.png") type="EXECVE"